16:20.663 --> 16:22.081
but, you know, if all of a sudden,

16:22.081 --> 16:24.867
it's all gone, there's nothing
left but the salt and the duds,

16:24.867 --> 16:27.369
well, you feel bad,
because if you'd known

16:27.369 --> 16:30.873
the last kernel was the last
one, you would've savored it.

16:32.841 --> 16:35.177
Am I making myself clear on this?

16:35.177 --> 16:38.047
Oh, yes, yes...

16:38.047 --> 16:39.548
Oh. I'm salt and duds.

16:42.551 --> 16:46.055
Well, I-I-I
don't know. I...

16:46.055 --> 16:49.058
