till the cows come home,

17:16.635 --> 17:20.506
but it won't alleviate the problem.

17:20.506 --> 17:21.924
After much consideration,

17:21.924 --> 17:24.810
I propose that you go on a flesh binge.

17:27.229 --> 17:29.181
Sow your wild oats.

17:29.181 --> 17:31.683
Get it out of your system.

17:31.683 --> 17:35.187
Savor your last kernel of popcorn.

17:37.106 --> 17:38.107
Are you serious?

17:38.107 --> 17:39.608
Absolutely.

17:39.608 --> 17:42.611
It's the only way we can
establish a clean slate.

17:42.611 --> 17:46.615
No guilt, no remorse, no regrets.

17:46.615 --> 17:48.000
So...

17:48.000 --> 17:51.336
