18:00.129 --> 18:01.880
You listen to me.

18:01.880 --> 18:06.051
I'm only going to agree to do
this because I love you, Diane.

18:09.354 --> 18:12.224
Well, don't do it for me, Sam.

18:12.224 --> 18:14.526
Do it for the health
