20:27.993 --> 20:30.495
Uh, good luck with your marriage.

20:30.495 --> 20:31.496
Yes. Thank you.

20:31.997 --> 20:32.998
Thank you. Thank you very much.

20:33.498 --> 20:34.499
Thank you, Rick.

20:35.000 --> 20:37.002
Well...

20:37.002 --> 20:39.004
I guess I'll just, uh...

20:39.004 --> 20:41.006
