20:41.006 --> 20:43.008
Uh, yeah, like hell you will!

20:43.008 --> 20:45.010
Sam? Now, Sam! Sam!

20:48.013 --> 20:48.880
All right.

20:48.880 --> 20:51.633
Where were you last night, hmm?

20:54.019 --> 20:57.522
