21:41.433 --> 21:42.434
You know why?

21:42.434 --> 21:44.936
Because I happen to be a one-woman guy.

21:44.936 --> 21:46.738
I mean, I mean,

21:46.738 --> 21:48.273
I think we got something
special going here,

21:48.273 --> 21:50.275
