it, like somebody else

21:50.776 --> 21:51.777
I could mention.

21:51.777 --> 21:55.747
You-you know, people could
refer to you as a tart.

21:58.667 --> 22:00.669
How can you say that?

22:00.669 --> 22:02.120
Easy. Tart!

22:02.120 --> 22:04.006
Tart, tart, tart, tart!

22:04.006 --> 22:05.173
I mean, what-what else

22:05.173 --> 22:06.875
